## Options

set n-completion-items 10
set font 'Source Code Pro @font_size@'
set guioptions ''
# set continuous-hist-save
set page-padding @page_padding@
# set smooth-scroll
set window-title-home-tilde
set window-title-page
set statusbar-home-tilde
set selection-clipboard 'clipboard'

## Key mappings

map [fullscreen] b navigate previous
map [presentation] b navigate previous

## Color settings

set completion-bg '#fce8c3'
